WEBVTT

00:00.552 --> 00:02.550
How much does a sunset weigh?

00:06.547 --> 00:08.086
How light is an emotion?

00:09.497 --> 00:11.323
The sudden feeling of freedom?

00:13.264 --> 00:17.433
What's the weight of a memory? Just an instance?

00:20.105 --> 00:26.569
So light, yet so intense, they stay in your mind forever.

00:31.161 --> 00:36.496
The more memories you want to keep, the lighter you need to be.

00:40.304 --> 00:42.871
And you, how far would you go?

00:46.153 --> 00:49.459
Travel lighter to go further with Samsonite.

